4.1.2 Problem Formulation

The objective is to augment the aggregate utility of the framework from the point of view of both InP and MVNOs. Therefore, our goal is to augment the income achieved by InP while at the same time taking care of the requests of MVNOs. Then, the VR allocation problem is given as follows:

